	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="8" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Dance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />終於要有新成員了，<tag a="110" b="6" />。<pageBreak /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呵呵，<delay20 />同伴增加果然是件<delay20 />令人開心的好事啊。</message>
	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="007_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今天會有新同伴搬來呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。<pageBreak /><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />隨著同伴增加，<delay20 />
<tag a="110" b="8" /><delay20 />也會變得更熱鬧，<delay20 />
所以我很開心喔。</message>
	<message label="007_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />！<delay20 />
新同伴搬來囉！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />第一印象可是很重要的喔。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以我打算先整理好儀容<delay20 />
再去打招呼。</message>
	<message label="007_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今天好像會有Rookie<delay20 />
搬來<tag a="110" b="8" />呢。<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />為了讓她早點習慣這座島的環境，<delay20 />
所以我也想回歸初衷，<delay20 />
對新來的女孩子溫柔點。<pageBreak /><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊，不對<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />即使不是女孩子，我也會很溫柔的，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="011" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="011_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />明天是
<tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />的Birthday！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />為了讓<gender3 m="他" f="她" />開心，<delay20 />
我準備了萬無一失的禮物！<10_4 />
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呵呵，<delay20 />真希望明天快點到～</message>
	<message label="011_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />的Birthday<delay20 />
就是明天了，<tag a="110" b="6" />。<pageBreak /><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你有準備禮物嗎？<10_4 />
<anim id="Dance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我的禮物十分Perfect喔！<pageBreak /><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我還一邊想著<gender3 m="他" f="她" />高興的樣子，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />做了許多事前排練喔。</message>
	<message label="011_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay20 />你知道嗎？<10_4 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />明天是<tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />的生日，<tag a="110" b="6" />。<pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我準備了超棒的禮物喔。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但我不奢求對方有所回報<tag a="110" b="0" />
真要說的話，<delay frames="40" /><anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我希望能看見<gender3 m="他" f="她" />的笑容。</message>
	<message label="013" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="013_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />越來越靠近<delay frames="40" /><tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" />
要搬走的日子<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />為了表達一直以來的感謝之情，<delay20 />
我想笑著送<gender3 m="他" f="她" />離開<tag a="110" b="0" /><10_4 />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />希望你也能不留遺憾地向<gender3 m="他" f="她" />道別，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="013_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" />明天就要離開<delay20 />
<tag a="110" b="8" />了，<tag a="110" b="6" />。<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果我說不會感到寂寞，那也是騙人的。<delay20 />
不過正是希望<gender3 m="他" f="她" />能夠幸福，<delay20 />
所以才想用笑容送<gender3 m="他" f="她" />一程。</message>
	<message label="013_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />剩下的時間也不多了<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />明天<tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" />就要
離開這座島了，<tag a="110" b="6" />。<pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我相信我們還能再見面的。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以現在該說的<delay20 />不是再見，<delay20 />
而是謝謝。</message>
